{"tid":2044352,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"48歲休班男督察粉嶺家中猝死","createTime":"2020-05-31T05:15:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T13:19:44.000Z","uid":23833,"like":226,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"aff5258d54c3a3b9055e284b844be1fb1ad4b8f0","tid":2044352,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T05:15:43.000Z","msg":"今早(31日)6時35分，粉嶺牽晴間一單位，一名男子跌倒昏迷，由父親發現報警。救援人員趕至，將事主送往北區醫院搶救，於早上7時54分證實不治。消息指，事主姓譚，48歲，為新界北總區交通部督察。事主因糖尿病、高血壓及慢性腎衰竭問題困擾，返朝九晚五的工作時間，亦沒有參與應付示威的工作。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200531/mobile/bkn-20200531115514508-0531_00822_001.html?fbclid=IwAR1QmDvU_MayZvv2rSKBf5Y7MkVz80KXnQWTgE3LPVW9e9OMz4NbW9CNoTc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200531%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200531115514508-0531_00822_001.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1QmDvU_MayZvv2rSKBf5Y7MkVz80KXnQWTgE3LPVW9e9OMz4NbW9CNoTc&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdIGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=7c8b95e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200531/mobile/bkn-20200531115514508-0531_00822_001.html?fbclid=IwAR1QmDvU_MayZvv2rSKBf5Y7MkVz80KXnQWTgE3LPVW9e9OMz4NbW9CNoTc</a>"},{"pid":"89c3a5a393cacde0a6828fe1289af1abe50774f8","tid":2044352,"uid":33643,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T05:17:12.000Z","msg":"雖然好想狙擊你，但我好開心"},{"pid":"046fb9da7dd8b1a77acfab024f44429b773d47be","tid":2044352,"uid":195350,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T05:17:51.000Z","msg":"咁要慶祝下"},{"pid":"6a12982cf4b0dcfea5a6a584ddf8f572cef08729","tid":2044352,"uid":31200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T05:18:03.000Z","msg":"RAP<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4880c53abdf121509b1ad3db8ff0da9b23bb689","tid":2044352,"uid":3302,"like":57,"dislike":2,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTim